{"tid":1459313,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人咳左好撚耐","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T05:25:51.000Z","uid":236000,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"95892e16472d3f6c45e7f94588644026c95c7ede","tid":1459313,"uid":236000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:53:55.000Z","msg":"728一次發夢無豬咀 個次的確食唔少 因為我留到最後包抄既時候入唔到地鐵<br />\n但我平時次次出去都有戴豬咀 仲係60926 真係咩都聞唔到<br />\n 唔知點解（好似真係自728個日）一直都咳緊到而家 仲要出一次返黎咳得嚴重過一次<br />\n硬食一晚會有咁大影響既咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n媽咪有煲個d淮山杞子 金銀花白菊花俾我飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知飲幾耐先唔咳<br />\n<br />\n希望我只係普通病左既 唔關D蛋事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58befb6c2c0583f54b292fa8e92846f253843913","tid":1459313,"uid":236000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:54:50.000Z","msg":"好似開錯台"},{"pid":"e678c663a0ac476b98710917f3fc0f91a7506716","tid":1459313,"uid":236000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:55:02.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"1532b773f77f0687be6a7de9ae04b01157fda03e","tid":1459313,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:55:13.000Z","msg":"快啲睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be1979d3c2708a59935eeaa5de1134d15e55236","tid":1459313,"uid":236000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:55:13.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"7cdcd57f5e2fbc8947ee962e25ea07db30678c9f","tid":1459313,"uid":236000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"e66a0a19def92ea9852b6b978d3330464b698ec1","tid":1